---
layout: base.njk
title: Writing
description: Writing on AWS security, threat detection, and cloud defence by Thomas Haggath.
---
<div class="blog-prose">
  <a href="/" class="back-link">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
    Back to CV
  </a>
  <h1>Writing</h1>
  <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:2rem;">AWS security, threat detection, and cloud defence.</p>

  {% if collections.posts.length %}
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <div class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
      {% if post.data.excerpt %}<p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>{% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% else %}
  <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">No posts yet. Check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
